text: José Ramos Castillo (born December 24, 1974 in Castellon De La Plana, Castellón) is a swimmer from Spain. He has a physical disability: he is an S7 type swimmer. In 2004, he lived in Artesa-onda, Castellón. He raced at the 2004 Summer Paralympics. He finished third in the 4 x 50 meter 20 points medley relay. == References == Category:Spanish swimmers Category:Living people Category:1974 births Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for Spain Category:People from the Valencian Community Category:2004 Summer Paralympics Category:Sportspeople with disabilities, type S7
